					<h4 class="rubric">
						<a href="http://www.newyorker.com/magazine/a-reporter-at-large" title="A Reporter at Large" itemprop="articleSection printSection">A Reporter at Large</a>
													<a href="http://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2014/02/17" title="Published in 2014-02-17" itemprop="printEdition">
