					<h1 itemprop="name headline">Cheap Words</h1>
					<h2>Amazon is good for customers. But is it good for books?</h2>
					<h3>By <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><a href="http://www.newyorker.com/contributors/george-packer" title="George Packer" rel="author" itemprop="name author">George Packer</a></span></h3>
